@RegressionTest
Feature: Clinical Note

  Scenario: To add a New Clinical Note and validates that note gets added.
    Given user is logged in with valid credentials
    And navigates to Engagement tab
    And clicks on Engagement id
    When user clicks on Clinical Note tab
    Then validates that Clinical Note tab is displayed
    When User clicks on Add New Clinical Note button
    Then validates that Clinical Note form is displayed
    And clicks on Cancel button on Clinical Note form
    Then validates that user should land on Engagement detail list page
    Then validates that new Clinical Note is not created
   
    When User clicks on Add New Clinical Note button
    Then validates that Clinical Note form is displayed
    And clicks on Electronically Sign button on Clinical Note
    Then validates that user should gets validation message
    And enters value for Subject on Clinical Note Page
    And enters value for Clinical Note on Clinical Note Page
    And verify the time is captured
    And clicks on Electronically Sign button on Clinical Note
    Then validate that Clinical Note is created

  Scenario: To Edit Clinical Note
    When clicks on Edit link for Clinical Note
    Then validates that Clinical Note form is displayed for Edit
    And selects value for status field
    And validates the values provided on view page
    And clicks on Electronically Sign button on Clinical Note
    Then validates that user should land on Engagement detail list page
    And user clicks on Show More link
    And close current tab for Clinical Note

  Scenario: To View Clinical Note
    When clicks on View link for Clinical Note
    Then validates that Clinical Note form is displayed for View
    Then validates all the fields on clinical note form
    And verify the time is captured for View form
    And clicks on Cancel button on Clinical Note form
    Then validates that user should land on Engagement detail list page

  Scenario: Show More
    When verify by defaults records for Clinical Note 
    And user clicks on Show More link
    Then more records are displayed successfully
    And clicks on Back to Related list link
    Then validates that user should land on Engagement detail list page
